description	"Dark Side Maurauder:
This Dark Jedi has a moderate range of offensive and defensive Force powers but is unequaled in the art of combat with the arcane double-bladed lightsaber.

^2Weaponry:
- Lightsaber (Staff)
-- Saber Defense 2
-- EX Saber Throw (2) ^3[CS1]
-- Blaster Defense (2) / Blaster Deflect (2)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (2)
- Push (2)
- Pull (1)
- Grip (3)
- Lightning (2)
- Dark Rage (3)

^8Attributes:
- Faster Movement
- Force Block/Focus (2)
- Bunny Hop (2)
- Slow Faller
"
